OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FSir David Beckham has received a star
OL,7,Fon the famous Hollywood Walk of Fame,
OL,8,Fjoining legendary athletes including
OL,9,FMuhammad Ali, Magic Johnson and Esther
OL,10,FWilliams.
OL,12,FThe former England captain and
OL,13,Ffootballer was recognised in a
OL,14,Fceremony on Friday for his role in
OL,15,Felevating the profile of 'soccer' in
OL,16,FAmerica, and his lasting influence on
OL,17,Fsport, entertainment and global
OL,18,Fculture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
