FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781308974
OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FSpeaking at the ceremony, the 51-year-
OL,7,Fold said he "could never have
OL,8,Fimagined" that he would receive a star
OL,9,Fon the Hollywood Walk of Fame as "a
OL,10,Fworking-class English soccer player".
OL,12,FSir David attended the event at 6819
OL,13,FHollywood Boulevard with his wife
OL,14,FVictoria and their children Romeo,
OL,15,FCruz and Harper.
OL,26,@oD@MOUpD@IO]qD@bOUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
