CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781308974
OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FTheir eldest son, Brooklyn, was not
OL,7,Fpresent amid an ongoing family feud
OL,8,Fwhen he accused his parents of "trying
OL,9,Fendlessly to ruin my relationship
OL,10,Fsince before my wedding" in a social
OL,11,Fmedia post in January.
OL,13,FNevertheless, Sir David thanked his
OL,14,F"incredible family" and "beautiful
OL,15,Fchildren", while reflecting on how
OL,16,F"mind-blowing" the achievement is.
OL,26,@pD@`OUrD@XO]vD@AOUvD@SO]vD@YOUwD@IO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
