PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781308974
OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FThe London-born star said: "I must
OL,7,Fadmit that this is all rather surreal.
OL,8,FI've experienced some amazing moments
OL,9,Fin my career, but to be here in Los
OL,10,FAngeles receiving a star on the world-
OL,11,Ffamous Walk of Fame is truly
OL,12,Fincredible.
OL,14,F"I grew up in the East End of London,
OL,15,Fa long way from Hollywood. As a young
OL,16,Fboy, I loved soccer more than anything
OL,17,Fand it was all I ever wanted to do. I
OL,18,Falways loved America, though, and its
OL,19,FTV shows."
OL,26,@nD@\OUvD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781308974
OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FHe continued: "I want to thank my
OL,7,Fincredible family, my parents and my
OL,8,Fsisters, who always supported my
OL,9,Fdreams.
OL,11,F"Victoria, my amazing wife of almost
OL,12,F30 years, without whom none of this
OL,13,Fwould be possible or enjoyable, and my
OL,14,Fbeautiful children, who are the reason
OL,15,Fthat I get out of bed in the morning."
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781308974
OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FHe grew emotional as he concluded his
OL,7,Fspeech, and said his "greatest
OL,8,Fachievement" was to make his children
OL,9,Fproud and he hoped they will "bring my
OL,10,Fgrandchildren here one day and tell
OL,11,Fthem about a boy who dreamed big".
OL,13,FHollywood star Tom Cruise was also at
OL,14,Fthe ceremony and praised Sir David's
OL,15,F20-year career ` in which he became
OL,16,Fthe first English player to win league
OL,17,Ftitles in four countries: England,
OL,18,FSpain, the United States and France.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@LO]qD@^OUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
