OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781308974
OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FSir David said: "I was obsessed with
OL,7,Faction heroes, so to stand here in
OL,8,Ffront of my friend Tom Cruise ` the
OL,9,Fgreatest movie star of our time ` is
OL,10,Fquite frankly mind-blowing."
OL,12,F"The fact that mine and Victoria's
OL,13,Ffirst movie date was Jerry Maguire is
OL,14,Fa pretty mad full circle moment," Sir
OL,15,FDavid added, referring to Cruise's
OL,16,Fstarring role in the hit 1996 romantic
OL,17,Fcomedy.
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@\O]tD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
