OL,3,CSir David Beckham receives star on the
OL,4,CHollywood Walk of Fame
OL,6,FLady Victoria Beckham also spoke at
OL,7,Fthe event and joked that she thought
OL,8,Fthe star was for her starring role in
OL,9,F1997 cult classic Spice World.
OL,11,FThe Spice Girls singer, nicknamed Posh
OL,12,FSpice, described the occasion as "so
OL,13,Fspecial" and hailed her husband's
OL,14,F"kindness, loyalty and commitment to
OL,15,Fthe people that he loves".
OL,17,FSir David has supported several
OL,18,Fcharitable causes, including serving
OL,19,Fas a goodwill ambassador for the
OL,20,Fhumanitarian aid organisation Unicef
OL,21,Fsince 2005.
OL,26,@tD@bOUuD@HO]vD@AOUwD@YO]
